{
  "stem": "22883.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he looked at that and said, very good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are hired.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in this way, I got the job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until the end.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after a day or two, I went there, this engineer, Meyer, asked her secretary, [SIGHS] Frau Fabianova, to arrange for us place in a-- in a camp for the-- for the volunteer workers.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the frame-- all the foreign workers, they had to live in, the Poles were forbidden to live privately.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So OK, she arranged it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She arranged in bribing the-- the-- the-- the camp [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] director or manager by giving him 200 cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when coming-- when I was coming from Warsaw to Kapfenburg, I-- I took with-- with me a few cartons of cigarettes because cigarettes was like [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], like money.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she gave 200, one carton of cigarettes to this guy and didn't ask any questions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we didn't have the-- all the documents, they-- they were left in this company, this Danish company in Kapfenburg.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had no documents here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we got the-- the shelter, and I got the job, and I think two days after, I went to-- there was a manager, a different manager, because this engineer was living in a different place.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] for our office, there was a-- a-- a special manager, and this manager was from Breslau, from Warsaw, now Polish city Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I-- I told him that with me is my wife, and I would like that she works in-- in the same office.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she agreed, and she asked me to-- to tell her to come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Lillian was, well, such an office help.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
